title: Who Is My R&B Singer Daddy?
text:
In celebrity seed news… 
Guess The Celebrity Parent A certain R&B crooner is showing off his beautiful 1-month-old baby girl. This singer is from a midwestern based 90s R&B group known for always being on the verge of what’s next.
Her dad, who’s newly married, is SO excited about her birth that he couldn’t help but show her off on Instagram.

Little Rory is the singer’s first child with his wifey.
Do YOU know the father of this sweet little girl?

Hit the flip.
